About Us
Crossroads Farm and Apiary offers strawberry picking in late winter and early spring as well as a fall festival in October. Throughout the year we have a working apiary providing honey for sale, bee sales, and pollination services. Our farm store is open at various times throughout the year for seasonal produce, honey, and farmhouse decor. We offer
group field
trips
and are committed to offering a space for our community to gather and learn about agriculture.
